What a real delight! Came here for a bit of business and pleasure and both were fantastically completed due to the central location of this wonderful flat.
The management team here were really nice. Upon advance booking and cost, which was very reasonable, they collected me from the airport.
Room was nice and cool from the moment I walked in. Nice day light views and very convenient with so many shops nearby.
I am a repeat visitor here and will be booking again very soon. !

info: Rating, 5 stars,  ¬∑ August 2022,  ¬∑ Stayed over a week
rating_comment: One month passed by so fast and felt like staying in our own house with a family of four. It was a wonderful experience.
